name: TagTest
description: Unit tests for the Tag class in the Jsoup parser, focusing on tag semantics, case sensitivity, and namespace handling.

test_cases.name: isCaseSensitive
test_cases.description: Tests if the Tag creation is case-sensitive.

test_cases.name: canBeInsensitive
test_cases.description: Tests if the Tag creation can be case-insensitive based on the locale.

test_cases.name: trims
test_cases.description: Tests if the Tag creation trims whitespace from the input.

test_cases.name: equality
test_cases.description: Tests the equality of Tags created with the same input.

test_cases.name: divSemantics
test_cases.description: Tests the semantic properties of the 'div' tag.

test_cases.name: pSemantics
test_cases.description: Tests the semantic properties of the 'p' tag.

test_cases.name: imgSemantics
test_cases.description: Tests the semantic properties of the 'img' tag.

test_cases.name: defaultSemantics
test_cases.description: Tests the default semantic properties for an undefined tag.

test_cases.name: valueOfChecksNotNull
test_cases.description: Tests if the Tag creation throws an exception for a null input.

test_cases.name: valueOfChecksNotEmpty
test_cases.description: Tests if the Tag creation throws an exception for an empty input.

test_cases.name: knownTags
test_cases.description: Tests the recognition of known tags.

test_cases.name: knownSvgNamespace
test_cases.description: Tests the namespace handling for known SVG tags.

test_cases.name: unknownTagNamespace
test_cases.description: Tests the namespace handling for unknown tags.
